{"tid":1434244,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要資訊] 北角狗屋用嘅係「防火網」","createTime":"2019-08-08T17:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T04:54:07.000Z","uid":270337,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"73d16221a5c7837591d7ef4c95e0b2e7922c47a4","tid":1434244,"uid":270337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:06:31.000Z","msg":"個白網係防火嘅，有狗試過用火機燒唔着<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要值成港幣70萬！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係知得咁多，唔知防火程度，唔知set嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔信嘅話可以推到叫記者問班狗驗証下我講嘅野<br />\n<br />\n講明先，一手料，我唔會答消息來源，雖然我P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007d1fb5bbbe0b04d0fe3d2bac11157b6a110c71","tid":1434244,"uid":189,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:09:06.000Z","msg":"應該為咗卸走俾人掟嘢啲力，隔一隔冇咁大破壞"},{"pid":"081d987e10139374ec02f104e12ae9e0ae648f03","tid":1434244,"uid":270337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"唔信就算，為保障當事人，我係唔會講source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92411afcffc9c99f31126ec3ef32e93709a858ef","tid":1434244,"uid":270337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"007d1fb5bbbe0b04d0fe3d2bac11157b6a110c71","tid":1434244,"uid":189,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:09:06.000Z","msg":"應該為咗卸走俾人掟嘢啲力，隔一隔冇咁大破壞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:11:14.000Z","msg":"本來我都以為係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97eb4a435d30584434b1ff90b3a527e54a56d418","tid":1434244,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:13:59.000Z","msg":"唔知防唔防蟲呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0b9a1d93de99dac7c10a87aa07eac901ae89f8","tid":1434244,"uid":270337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco